{
  "stem": "24515.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't know if it'd be true for everybody, but for me, it worked out very nicely, thank you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I played with my brother quite a bit, you know, imaginative games.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I read quite a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was some schoolwork, some homework.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And that was about as far as it g-- went, as far as I know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By and large, I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Interestingly enough, even under the Nazis-- you see, my elementary school period ended in '33.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was 11 and went to this humanistic gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The point was that this was known as a staatsgymnasium, the state gymnasium, which meant that it was under the direct control of the state of Saxony, you see, province.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the other schools, high schools, were under the control of the municipality of Chemnitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This gave the faculty and the director of the school some leeway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now for example, we stayed in the-- the few Jews who were there were kept in this staatsgymnasium longer than any other Jew.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the faculty, as far as they could, did, somehow protect ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I recall a little story which is, I suppose, half funny and half serious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I came in one day, and on my desk were all kinds of remarks chalked in, in chalk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And also the the newspaper was there. was a newspaper which was [GERMAN], and it was a pornographic thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a, you know-- telling you how awful the Jews were and so on, so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was on many street corners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had their reading box, and I always stayed and looked at it and read it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think I was the only one who did.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
